---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { site } from '../site.config';
---

<Base title="About" description={site.meta.about}>
  <p class="prompt-line"><span class="prompt">$</span> cat about.md</p>
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p class="lede">
    A short paragraph or two introducing yourself. Where you grew up, what you
    studied, what kind of work you have ended up doing, and what currently has
    your attention. Resist the urge to write a resume here &mdash; that is what
    the resume page is for.
  </p>

  <p>
    A second paragraph for color. The things you find interesting outside of
    work, the way you like to spend a Saturday, the type of problem that hooks
    you for a weekend. Recruiters skim this; the right teammates read it.
  </p>

  <h2>Now</h2>
  <p>
    A <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">now page</a>
    style block: what you are reading, building, learning, or thinking about
    right now. Update it every month or two so it stays honest.
  </p>

  <ul class="now-list">
    <li><span class="now-key">reading</span> <span class="now-val">Designing Data-Intensive Applications</span></li>
    <li><span class="now-key">building</span> <span class="now-val">This website</span></li>
    <li><span class="now-key">learning</span> <span class="now-val">Rust, slowly</span></li>
    <li><span class="now-key">listening</span> <span class="now-val">Nils Frahm on repeat</span></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
  <ul class="elsewhere">
    <li><a href={site.social.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github</a></li>
    <li><a href={site.social.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">linkedin</a></li>
    <li><a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>email</a></li>
  </ul>
</Base>

<style>
  .prompt-line {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  h1 { margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .lede { max-width: 60ch; }
  p { max-width: 60ch; }

  .now-list, .elsewhere {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .now-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border-muted);
  }

  .now-key {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    min-width: 6rem;
  }

  .now-val {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .elsewhere {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
